My code ispired from the book OpenGL Programming Guide: The Official Guide to Learning OpenGL, Versions 3.0 and 3.1 (7th Edition).

ISBN-13: 978-0321552624


Prerequsities (on Ubuntu):
gcc
cmake >= 2.8.2
libsdl1.2.dev

and an openGL capable card.

Compilation: In the same directory where this README is run:
cmake . && make

To execute:
./bin/main

Enjoy!

